Package com.example.cs213_tuition_project_javafx

Class Date

java.lang.Object
com.example.cs213_tuition_project_javafx.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
Implements our date object as a comparable object. Consists of three integer components: year, month, day. Overrides for equals, toString, and compareTo. Implements methods to check if dates are valid, or year is a LeapYear.
